init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's also a shapeshifter, and he's been using his ability to look like other men to get close to her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She's unaware that he's been using his ability to look like other men to get close to her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's been trying to change himself to be the perfect man for her.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: One day, while he's in his human form, she sees something that makes her suspicious.
